<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="output.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 via-white to-blue-200 flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4 py-12">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-blue-800 mb-8 drop-shadow-lg tracking-wide animate-pulse"><%= title %></h1>
        <div class="max-w-3xl w-full bg-white/90 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-12 border-4 border-blue-200 backdrop-blur-lg">
            <p class="text-2xl text-gray-800 mb-8 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                Welcome to <span class="font-bold text-blue-700 underline decoration-blue-400">Rent Home</span>! We are dedicated to making your home rental experience <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">simple</span>, <span class="text-green-600 font-semibold">secure</span>, and <span class="text-purple-600 font-semibold">convenient</span>.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
                Our platform connects tenants and landlords, offering a wide range of rental properties to suit every need and budget. Whether you're searching for your next home or looking to list your property, we've got you covered.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 space-y-3 pl-4">
                <li><span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Verified</span> property listings</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Easy</span> search and filter options</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Secure</span> communication between tenants and landlords</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Responsive</span> customer support</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 font-semibold">
                Thank you for choosing <span class="font-bold text-blue-700 underline decoration-blue-400">Rent Home</span>. Your perfect home is just a few clicks away!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>